
| Feature / Model      | BERT                                                    | GPT                               | T5                                 |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| **Full Name**        | Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers | Generative Pretrained Transformer | Text-to-Text Transfer Transformer  |
| **Developed by**     | Google AI                                               | OpenAI                            | Google Research                    |
| **Year Introduced**  | 2018                                                    | 2018                              | 2020                               |
| **Architecture**     | Encoder-only                                            | Decoder-only                      | Encoder-Decoder (full Transformer) |
| **Pretraining Task** | Masked Language Modeling (MLM)                          | Causal Language Modeling (CLM)    | MLM + many others (multitask)      |
| **Use Case Type**    | Understanding                                           | Generation                        | Both (flexible)                    |
| **Typical Tasks**    | Classification, Q\&A, NER                               | Text generation, chatbots         | Q\&A, summarization, translation   |
| **Input Format**     | Plain sentence                                          | Prompts or plain sentences        | Input + Task label as text         |
| **Output Format**    | Sentence-level output                                   | Text continuation                 | Any text                           |
| **Popular Variants** | RoBERTa, DistilBERT, ALBERT                             | GPT-2, GPT-3, GPT-4               | mT5, FLAN-T5                       |





ðŸ§ª When to Use What?
Goal	                                     Model
Text classification	                     BERT
Summarization	                             T5
Chatbot or text generation	             GPT
Multilingual translation	             mT5 (T5 variant)
Extract info from documents	             BERT
Flexible multi-task setup	             T5


